  "title": "URGENT: Field Engineer x3 (equipment/semicon/mfg)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Perform on-site troubleshooting, maintenance, and repair of equipment and systems</p></li><li><p>Analyze equipment performance data and implement preventative maintenance measures</p></li><li><p>Provide technical support and training to production teams</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with cross-functional teams to resolve complex issues and optimize operations</p></li><li><p>Maintain detailed records and documentation of all activities</p></li><li><p>Ensure adherence to safety protocols and environmental regulations</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>What we're looking for</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma / Degree in Mechanical Engineering or a related technical field</p></li><li><p>Minimum 3 years of experience as a Field Engineer in the semiconductor or manufacturing industry</p></li><li><p>Strong troubleshooting and problem-solving skills with the ability to work independently</p></li><li><p>Proficient in the use of diagnostic tools and equipment</p></li><li><p>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills to interact with diverse stakeholders</p></li><li><p>Flexible work schedule and willingness to work in a dynamic, fast-paced environment</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, please click on <strong>“Apply Now”</strong> or submit your resume to <a href=\"mailto:ref68@trustrecruit.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>ref68@trustrecruit.com.sg</strong></a></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website www.trustrecruit.com.sg </p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: John Angeline</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R1544851</p>",
